---
title: Applewood Smoked Steak with Foil-Pouch Potatoes and Bacon Caesar Salad
description: Steak and bacon, what could be better? This steak gets the smokehouse treatment with our delicious Applewood Smoke spice. A bacon caesar salad and grilled foil-pouch potatoes perfect this meal for the last long weekend of summer!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/applewood-smoked-steak-62dbd16f.jpg
